    <h1>Exam Application System</h1>

    <h3>1. Title and Scope</h3>
    <p><strong>Title:</strong> Exam Application System</p>
    <p><strong>Scope:</strong> This system manages exams for students in an educational institution. It handles students, subjects, questions, scheduling, and tracking performance — all accessible via a secure web-based backend built with Node.js and MySQL.</p>

    <h3>2. Purpose / Objective</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Manage student and admin data securely</li>
      <li>Schedule exams by subject and date</li>
      <li>Create questions and associate them with exams</li>
      <li>Record and analyze student performance</li>
      <li>Support subject-student and exam-student relationships</li>
      <li>Provide API access via secure authentication (JWT)</li>
    </ul>
